<subSubSection pageId="13" pageNumber="371" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="13.[151,1437,151,1761]" pageId="13" pageNumber="371">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,1699,1725]" pageId="13" pageNumber="371">Etymology.</emphasis>
The specific epithet is derived from the Latin 
<emphasis box="[853,984,1699,1724]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="371">purpuratus,</emphasis>
referring to the purplish black markings of the forewing.
</paragraph>
